msgid "Membership Fee Structure"
msgstr "Structuur lidmaatschapsgeld"

#: ../../source/governing-docs/membership-fee-structure.rst:4
msgid ""
"This document outlines the current structure of membership fees for the KNA-"
"RNAS. The fees may be modified by a vote of the Annual Members Meeting."
